      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to show you this absolute beauty. It has been pampered since day one and is in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and kept in tip-top shape, this is the one for you. Come by and take a look, I'd love to show it off!",
