      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, with the original deep-gloss paint preserved under a professional ceramic coating\u2014free of any rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple with zero bolster wear, and the 'new car' scent persists. Every electronic feature, from the infotainment system to the ambient lighting, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in peak condition, backed by a comprehensive, folder-organized service history documenting every maintenance milestone. With remarkably low mileage and a spotless engine bay, this is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a flawless, turn-key example of automotive excellence.",
